---
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Delete Your Account - OurCouple" description="How to delete your OurCouple account and all associated data." canonicalPath="/delete-account">
  <Header />

  <main class="flex-1 pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text mb-8">Delete Your Account</h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary mb-8">We're sorry to see you go. Here's how to delete your OurCouple account and what happens when you do.</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Option 1: From the App</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            The fastest way to delete your account is directly from the app:
          </p>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-3 ml-4">
            <li>Open OurCouple</li>
            <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong> (last tab)</li>
            <li>Scroll to the bottom</li>
            <li>Tap <strong>"Delete My Account"</strong></li>
            <li>Confirm the deletion</li>
          </ol>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-4">
            Your account and all associated data will be permanently deleted.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Option 2: By Email</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            If you no longer have access to the app, you can request account deletion by email:
          </p>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-3 ml-4">
            <li>Send an email to <a href="mailto:contact@vynse.dev?subject=Account%20Deletion%20Request" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark">contact@vynse.dev</a></li>
            <li>Use the subject line: <strong>"Account Deletion Request"</strong></li>
            <li>Include the email address associated with your OurCouple account</li>
          </ol>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-4">
            We will process your request and delete your account within <strong>30 days</strong>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">What Gets Deleted</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            When you delete your account, the following data is <strong>permanently deleted</strong>:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Your account and profile information (name, email)</li>
            <li>All your messages and photos of the day</li>
            <li>All your shared moments and memories</li>
            <li>All your notes</li>
            <li>All your events</li>
            <li>Your daily question answers</li>
            <li>Your virtual pet data</li>
            <li>Your push notification tokens</li>
            <li>Your app preferences and settings</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">What Happens to Shared Content</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            Since OurCouple is a shared space between two partners:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Content you authored will be removed from the shared space</li>
            <li>Your partner's own content remains in their account</li>
            <li>Your partner will be notified that you left the couple space</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>All personal data is permanently deleted within <strong>30 days</strong></li>
            <li>Anonymized crash logs may be retained for app stability purposes</li>
            <li>No personal or identifiable data is kept after deletion</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Important Notes</h2>
          <div class="bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-4">
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2">
              <li>Account deletion is <strong>permanent and irreversible</strong></li>
              <li>Because your content is encrypted, we cannot recover it after deletion</li>
              <li>If you have an active premium subscription, please cancel it through your app store (Apple App Store or Google Play Store) before deleting your account to avoid future charges</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            Questions about account deletion? Contact us:
          </p>
          <p class="text-primary font-medium">
            <a href="mailto:contact@vynse.dev">contact@vynse.dev</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
        <a href="/" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark transition-colors font-medium">
          ‚Üê Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
